🧠 KEY EFE INSIGHTS:
• Expected Utility (Pragmatic): How much the agent expects to like predicted outcomes
• Epistemic Value: How much the agent expects to learn (exploration)
• EFE balances exploitation (utility) vs exploration (information gain)
• Lower EFE actions are more preferred
• PyMDP control.py uses similar EFE calculations for policy inference

